    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You fling psychic material, called ectoplasm, at the target, making a ranged attack against its KAC and dealing bludgeoning damage. Each projectile in the barrage has the @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.O5GDQUKPCJ9Zbnfj]{Knockdown} critical hit effect. In addition, ectoplasm extends to the Ethereal Plane, so it affects ethereal and incorporeal creatures.</p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">1st:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> When you cast ectoplasmic barrage as a 1st-level spell, each projectile deals 2d6 damage on a hit.</span></p>\n<p><strong>2nd:</strong> When you cast ectoplasmic barrage as a 2nd-level spell, each projectile deals 4d6 damage on a hit.</p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">3rd:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> When you cast ectoplasmic barrage as a 3rd-level spell, each projectile deals 7d6 damage on a hit.</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">4th:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> When you cast ectoplasmic barrage as a 4th-level spell, each projectile deals 10d6 damage on a hit.</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">5th:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> When you cast ectoplasmic barrage as a 5th-level spell, each projectile deals 13d6 damage on a hit. A struck target is also @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.nFBcsp5FS1Wi46Fc]{Entangled} for 1 round.</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">6th:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;When you cast&nbsp;ectoplasmic barrage&nbsp;as a 6th-level spell, each projectile deals 15d6 damage on a hit. A struck target is also @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.nFBcsp5FS1Wi46Fc]{Entangled} for 1d4 rounds.</span></p>"
